      <title>墨西哥当选总统承诺为墨西哥中部制定水资源计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/mexico-water-crisis-president-elect-sheinbaum-pledges-plan-for-central-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥当选总统克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆誓言要在墨西哥中部实施一项大规模水资源计划，这是解决水资源分配不均和频繁干旱问题的国家战略的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/mexico-water-crisis-president-elect-sheinbaum-pledges-plan-for-central-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 03:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Haven Rush、“特朗普交易”在枪击事件后影响投资者心态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/haven-rush-trump-trades-on-investor-minds-after-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场观察人士表示，在前总统唐纳德·特朗普在集会上遭枪击后，交易员们首先会涌入避险资产，并重新评估与其候选人资格最相关的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/haven-rush-trump-trades-on-investor-minds-after-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 03:10:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件增加其连任几率，比特币上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/bitcoin-btc-rises-as-trump-rally-shooting-seen-increasing-re-election-odds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普集会发生枪击事件后，比特币上涨，引发人们猜测该事件将增加他赢得总统大选的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/bitcoin-btc-rises-as-trump-rally-shooting-seen-increasing-re-election-odds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 02:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普集会期间遭枪击受伤，各国领导人作出反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/world-leaders-react-after-trump-injured-in-shooting-at-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，前总统唐纳德·特朗普在集会上遭枪击受伤，至少一名参加者死亡，世界各国领导人谴责政治暴力，并祝愿特朗普早日康复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/world-leaders-react-after-trump-injured-in-shooting-at-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 02:41:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对总统和候选人的袭击如何影响美国历史</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/how-attacks-on-presidents-and-candidates-have-shaped-us-history</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，前总统唐纳德·特朗普遭枪击，这只是最近发生的一起影响美国历史的政治暴力行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/how-attacks-on-presidents-and-candidates-have-shaped-us-history</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 02:36:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普枪击事件后血腥、叛逆的形象激发了他的支持者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/trump-shooting-ex-president-s-bloodied-defiant-image-pumps-up-gop-base</link>
